  <span id="freeText9542128784025411938" style="display:none">I think about Hitch all the time. I don't know how long it took for my jaw to close after I first heard him deliver an opening 20 minutes to a debate group. We can only imagine in our own Hitchens-inspired minds about what he'd be writing these last few years. His voice is so needed and sorely missed.</span>
