        <div class="reviewText stacked">
              <span id="reviewTextContainer262340756" class="readable"
              >
            
<span id="freeTextContainer438428326514695205">A nice, short primer for Christopher Hitchens. RIP. This is one of those books I think everyone should read. Skepticism, disputation and contrarianism is underrated and underutilized.</span>

          </span>
        </div>


