<span id="freeTextContainer2128294767630827471">This book underscores what I like about Christopher Hitchens: he confronts every ideology, pissing off both liberals and conservatives. If I don&apos;t always agree with him, I always admire his iconoclasm and his style of disputation.</span>
  <span id="freeText2128294767630827471" style="display:none">This book underscores what I like about Christopher Hitchens: he confronts every ideology, pissing off both liberals and conservatives. If I don't always agree with him, I always admire his iconoclasm and his style of disputation.</span>
